                                        <height quantity="000"/>
                                        <width quantity="000"/>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </extent>
                                <foliation>Foliation in Arabic numerals. Fol. 1 (flyleaf) is upside
                                    down. Foliation also in Hebrew characters: fol. 3 = fol.
                                        <foreign xml:lang="he">ב</foreign>. Lacuna between fols. 88
                                    and 89? (one folio is missing according to Hebrew foliation,
                                    catchword does not match). From fol. 327 Hebrew foliation does
                                    not match Arabic numerals: fol. 327 = fol. <foreign xml:lang="he">שכג</foreign> - fol. 340 = fol. <foreign xml:lang="he">שכו</foreign>.</foliation>
                            </supportDesc>
